snippet: Rafael Nadal won his first match after being away for more than seven months because of a knee injury, teaming with Juan Monaco to defeat Frantisek Cermak and Lukas Dlouhy, 6-3, 6-2.
abstract: Rafael Nadal wins his first match after being away for more than seven months because of knee injury, teaming with Juan Monaco to defeat Frantisek Cermak and Lukas Dlouhy in clay-court tournament.
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal won his first match after being away for more than seven months because of a knee injury, teaming with Juan Monaco to defeat Frantisek Cermak and Lukas Dlouhy, 6-3, 6-2.
